{"tid":2186021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得蕭生真係好勁","createTime":"2020-09-02T15:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T16:03:40.000Z","uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9791e650b179389c12e1f9750651b6cbbcb45c19","tid":2186021,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"好多人忙緊奮鬥升職 讀書入u 維持生活果陣<br />\n<br />\n佢好似唔洗做咁日日9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做餐廳既話佢都叫搞左時代韓系完左夢<br />\n<br />\n做電影又叫搞過唐伯虎 都好出名<br />\n<br />\n讀書又hku<br />\n<br />\n打工又做過高層<br />\n<br />\n做政治都算首席深黃 冇咩人懷疑佢扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做網台又出名 <br />\n<br />\n好多人追求一世只想完夢既野佢都達成左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要非父幹咁有錢去搞飲食 超市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52a735773a67e330fbd7d860eab5a545d900c55","tid":2186021,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:47:57.000Z","msg":"人地都有打工 創業過<br />\n你睇人半退休階段做乜"},{"pid":"e0aa460b1a2977951321e9e289aa78adacefc648","tid":2186021,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:55:38.000Z","msg":"唯燈不破<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3046e0aed5250a47bc5edda37f30d952babe5907","tid":2186021,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f52a735773a67e330fbd7d860eab5a545d900c55","tid":2186021,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:47:57.000Z","msg":"人地都有打工 創業過<br />\n你睇人半退休階段做乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"佢後生應該都好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人onon99又一日"},{"pid":"9b78a4170ed093c1f650b85d8b5b0fd22df46980","tid":2186021,"uid":108225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3046e0aed525